\c 28
\s UHananiya utshumayela amanga
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngalowomnyaka,\x + 27.12.\x* ekuqaleni kokubusa kukaZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda, ngomnyaka wesine, ngenyanga yesihlanu, uHananiya\x + 36.12; 37.13.\x* indodana kaAzuri umprofethi\x + Hez. 11.1.\x* owayengoweGibeyoni\x + Josh.9.3; 21.17.\x* wakhuluma kimi endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* emehlweni abapristi labantu bonke, esithi:
\v 2 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, isithi: Ngilephulile ijogwe lenkosi yeBhabhiloni.\x + 25.12; 32.5.\x*
\v 3 Kusesephakathi kweminyaka emibili yezinsuku ngizabuyisela kulindawo\x + 27.16.\x* izitsha zonke zendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*,\x + 27.16.\x* uNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni azisusa kulindawo wazisa eBhabhiloni.
\v 4 Futhi uJekoniya indodana kaJehoyakhimi inkosi yakoJuda, labo bonke abathunjwa bakoJuda, abaya eBhabhiloni, ngiza\add ba\add*buyisela kulindawo, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*; ngoba ngizalephula ijogwe lenkosi yeBhabhiloni.\x + 27.2,11,12; 28 .4,10,11,12.\x*
\p
\v 5 Wasekhuluma uJeremiya umprofethi kuHananiya umprofethi emehlweni abapristi lemehlweni abantu bonke ababemi endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*;
\v 6 uJeremiya umprofethi wasesithi: Ameni!\x + 1 Kho. 1.36.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* kayenze njalo, iN\nd kosi\nd* kayiqinise amazwi akho owaprofethileyo, ukuthi ibuyise izitsha zendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, labo bonke abathunjwa, kusuke eBhabhiloni kuze kulindawo.
\v 7 Kodwa ake uzwe lelilizwi engilikhuluma endlebeni zakho lendlebeni zabo bonke abantu:
\v 8 Abaprofethi ababephambi kwami lababephambi kwakho kwasendulo baprofetha bemelene lamazwe amanengi bemelene lemibuso emikhulu, ngempi langobubi langomatshayabhuqe wesifo.
\v 9 Umprofethi oprofetha\x + Dute. 18.22.\x* ngokuthula,\x + 6.14.\x* lapho ilizwi lomprofethi selifikile, lowomprofethi uzakwaziwa ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* imthumile ngeqiniso.
\p
\v 10 Umprofethi uHananiya waselisusa ijogwe entanyeni kaJeremiya umprofethi, walephula.\x + 27.2; 28.2. 1 Kho. 22.11.\x*
\v 11 UHananiya wasekhuluma emehlweni abantu bonke esithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngokunjalo ngizalephula ijogwe likaNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 27.2,11,12; 28 .4,10,11,12. 27.12.\x* ngilisuse entanyeni yezizwe zonke kusesephakathi kweminyaka emibili yezinsuku.\x + 27.7.\x* UJeremiya umprofethi wasehamba ngendlela yakhe.
\p
\v 12 Laselifika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuJeremiya, emva kokuthi uHananiya umprofethi esephulile ijogwe elisusa entanyeni kaJeremiya umprofethi,\x + 27.2; 28.2. 1 Kho. 22.11.\x* lisithi:
\v 13 Hamba u\add ye\add*tshela uHananiya usithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Wephulile amajogwe esigodo; kodwa uzawenza amajogwe ensimbi endaweni yawo.
\v 14 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Ngigaxile ijogwe lensimbi\x + Dute. 28.48.\x* entanyeni yazo zonke lezizizwe\x + 27.7.\x* ukuze zisebenzele uNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni; futhi zizamsebenzela,\x + 25.11.\x* njalo ngimnikile lezinyamazana zeganga.\x + 27.6.\x*
\p
\v 15 UJeremiya umprofethi wasesithi kuHananiya umprofethi: Ake uzwe, Hananiya; iN\nd kosi\nd* kayikuthumanga,\x + 29.31.\x* kodwa wena wenza lababantu ukuthi bathembe\x + 29.31.\x* amanga.\x + 20.6. Hez. 13.22.\x*
\v 16 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangela, ngizakuxotsha ebusweni bomhlaba; lonyaka uzakufa, ngoba ukhulumile ukuhlamuka umelene leN\nd kosi\nd*.\x + 29.32. Dute. 13.5.\x*
\v 17 Wafa-ke uHananiya umprofethi ngalowomnyaka ngenyanga yesikhombisa.
